 sound. As for the speed of the sounds, it has to sweep fast enough so that=
 it does not predominantly catch any whole words or phrases of radio broadc=
ast that can be mistaken for spirit communication. And the theory is that t=
he spirit will use the small broken up fragments of speech to form complete=
